  "page": "House Dryland",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Dryland of Hellgate Hall</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Hellgate_Hall\" title=\"Hellgate Hall\">Hellgate Hall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nExtinct</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Brimstone\" title=\"King of the Brimstone\">King of the Brimstone</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Hellgate_Hall\" title=\"Lord of Hellgate Hall\">Lord of Hellgate Hall</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\nnone</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died out</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar_migration\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rhoynar migration\">Rhoynar migration</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Dryland of Hellgate Hall</b> is an extinct noble house from <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> who ruled as <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Brimstone\" title=\"King of the Brimstone\">Kings</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brimstone\" title=\"Brimstone\">Brimstone</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Hellgate_Hall\" title=\"Hellgate Hall\">Hellgate Hall</a>. Their arms are not yet given.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Historical_Members\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Historical Members</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Dryland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Lucifer_Dryland\" title=\"Lucifer Dryland\">Lucifer Dryland</a>, the last of his line, was one of the six defeated kings sent to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Martell\" title=\"Mors Martell\">Mors Martell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Historical_Members\">Historical Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Dryland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Historical Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Lucifer_Dryland\" title=\"Lucifer Dryland\">Lucifer Dryland</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Dryland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lucifer, the Brimstone, and Hellgate Hall are references by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucifer\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Lucifer\">Lucifer</a>, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fire_and_brimstone\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fire and brimstone\">brimstone</a> and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hell\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Hell\">Hell</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Dryland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The